Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.37,0:01:04.34,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,我知道你一定不会原谅手上沾满你弟弟鲜血的我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.34,0:01:05.66,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,再见了 英二
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.67,0:01:07.20,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,再见了 盖尔前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.96,0:01:45.10,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,怎么能让你们把我们丢到太空里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.40,0:01:46.99,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,要杀就在这里杀了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.40,0:01:48.69,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,快给我进去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.91,0:01:50.32,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,要开枪就在这开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.32,0:01:50.87,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,大卫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.69,0:01:56.84,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,被外星人捉走 我们的命运就好像风中残烛一样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.20,0:02:02.57,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,可是 上天还是没有放弃我们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.10,0:02:08.67,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,我们之中有人特别受上天疼爱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.67,0:02:11.84,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,我是这么觉得的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.84,0:02:12.48,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,把枪丢掉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.64,0:02:17.62,Layzner_Title,Eiji,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,760)}变成苍之流星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.23,0:02:34.06,Default_Sub,Soldier,0,0,0,,救到卡露拉少尉了 现在要回航了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.06,0:02:38.74,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,英二 你以为靠你自己真的能活下去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.96,0:02:42.47,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,太可惜了 那太难了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.13,0:02:54.02,Default_Sub,Officer,0,0,0,,回收到卡露拉少尉了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.03,0:02:58.49,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,好 本舰的损坏状况呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.75,0:03:01.72,Default_Sub,Officer,0,0,0,,戒备中 现在在维修中 马上就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.72,0:03:03.38,Default_Sub,Off2,0,0,0,,报告 修理好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.38,0:03:05.62,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,好 马上追击
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.93,0:03:20.72,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,盖尔中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.31,0:03:22.01,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,没受伤吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.84,0:03:26.46,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.97,0:03:33.58,Default_Sub,Solider,0,0,0,,少尉 请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.99,0:03:39.89,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,我自己闯的祸 我自己负责
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.34,0:03:42.12,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,我不会让你死的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.12,0:03:45.14,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,我 如果我做的事你无法原谅的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.45,0:03:47.73,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,请中尉您杀了我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.85,0:03:50.47,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.52,0:04:04.75,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,本舰的负责人是我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.52,0:04:10.47,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,所以在本舰发生的任何事都由我负责
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.01,0:04:11.90,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.93,0:04:18.88,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,追击航天飞机的事就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.36,0:04:21.63,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,为了准备等一下的战斗我要先休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.41,0:04:40.21,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,我一定要亲手打倒英二
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.82,0:05:13.57,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,盖尔中尉 只要是为了你 我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.13,0:05:27.26,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,看样子好像得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.26,0:05:29.36,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,一定是上天在保佑我们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.36,0:05:31.08,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,亚瑟 肚子好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.57,0:05:36.55,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,那个啊 我每次一紧张就会肚子痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.55,0:05:38.14,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,我很敏感对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.15,0:05:40.42,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,你有自知之明真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.42,0:05:43.58,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,你太失礼了 我从十三岁开始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.33,0:05:48.33,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,亚瑟 你还真是老实
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.46,0:05:54.13,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,可是我妈妈说十三岁还算正常 对吧 博士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.13,0:05:55.36,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.06,0:06:01.97,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,安静一点 电脑正在计算
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.36,0:06:03.76,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,计算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.06,0:06:06.14,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,算出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.14,0:06:11.68,Default_Sub,Com,0,0,0,,目标距离 有97.62%概率会被追击舰截获
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.52,0:06:13.29,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.00,0:06:18.27,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,就是说我们在到达最短距离前就会被追击队捉到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.00,0:06:21.96,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,怎么会这样 这么说我们逃不掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.96,0:06:25.23,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,那船装有「星际驱动」系统的引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.96,0:06:25.23,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(695,980)}Inter-Planet Drive
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.58,0:06:27.64,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,现在你们也看到电脑计算的结果了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.98,0:06:31.18,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,所以我们不要再吵了 快想办法逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.69,0:06:32.87,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,如果被捉到的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.07,0:06:35.93,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,这次我们一定会被
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.34,0:06:39.01,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,你的意思是我们会被干掉是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.01,0:06:41.34,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,好痛 我的肚子又 好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.92,0:06:53.58,Default_Sub_Top,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,我是隶属于联合国宇宙局的伊丽莎白·克蕾布里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.88,0:06:55.44,Default_Sub_Top,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,月球基地请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.44,0:06:59.22,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,美国和苏联军的舰队都因为外星人而全灭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.22,0:07:02.24,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,现在我们也正在被外星人追击中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.24,0:07:03.91,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,请求紧急救援
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.33,0:07:09.74,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,为什么没有回应
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.98,0:07:12.24,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,从这传电波又不需要几十分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.85,0:07:15.53,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,早知道那时候应该再多破坏一下的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.66,0:07:17.86,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,我们那时候哪有那么多时间啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.86,0:07:19.46,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,可是如果再破坏一下的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.46,0:07:22.91,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,这样的话 我们那时候就被杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.83,0:07:41.80,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,如果回地球的话 好想洗个热水澡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.42,0:07:44.94,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,用玫瑰香味的洗发水洗头
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.99,0:07:52.74,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,再穿上最喜欢的丝绸礼服 然后再去约会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.00,0:07:54.08,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,跟谁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.80,0:07:57.54,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,这个嘛 跟谁好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.52,0:08:03.55,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,我怎么样 如果回去的话 请跟我交往
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.55,0:08:05.08,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.13,0:08:07.28,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,我要先跟爸爸交往
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.66,0:08:09.68,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,那爸爸之后换我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.68,0:08:11.25,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.25,0:08:14.64,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,好 大卫 来猜拳嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.42,0:08:19.91,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,干嘛 别装了  你不也想跟她约会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.91,0:08:21.13,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.13,0:08:23.83,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,光明正大地像个绅士般来猜拳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.83,0:08:27.28,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,好 这有趣 亚瑟 来猜拳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.59,0:08:30.42,Default_Sub,D&A,0,0,0,,石头剪子布
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.60,0:08:34.84,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,两个人都加油 我答应你们跟赢的人先约会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.84,0:08:37.35,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,设法要突破这沉重的恐怖感 大家的心中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.35,0:08:42.96,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,我可以感觉到大家的悲痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.96,0:08:45.90,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,赢了 我能先和西蒙尼约会了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.75,0:08:48.50,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,伊丽莎白博士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.29,0:08:51.38,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.44,0:09:02.36,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,那星球
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.64,0:09:06.88,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,那就是地球对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.88,0:09:09.65,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,对啊 那就是我们的故乡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.19,0:09:12.15,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,那就是我们的目标星球
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.66,0:09:16.30,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,真的是地球
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.60,0:09:17.41,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,是我们的星球
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.49,0:09:18.53,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,终于回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.73,0:09:31.21,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,在宇宙这一片黑暗的海中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.55,0:09:35.14,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,温柔地闪耀着蔚蓝色光芒的星球 地球
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.60,0:09:39.89,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,重新发现地球
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.89,0:09:42.89,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,好像让我们心中涌起了愉快的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.36,0:09:45.99,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,英二
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.56,0:10:07.00,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,你一定不会原谅手中沾满你弟弟的血的我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.18,0:10:10.92,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,再见了 玖丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.00,0:10:18.71,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,这样下去会被追上的 快想点办法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.73,0:10:20.71,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,速度没办法再快了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.71,0:10:21.77,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.98,0:10:22.76,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,大卫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.89,0:10:24.91,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,只有战斗一途了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.13,0:10:27.53,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,请跟我换一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.53,0:10:29.10,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,亚瑟 拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.36,0:10:34.19,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,检测到目标了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.81,0:10:37.52,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,保持速度 跟太空船平行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.52,0:10:38.23,Default_Sub,Off,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.62,0:10:39.41,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.41,0:10:42.57,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,盖尔中尉 请让我一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.20,0:10:47.66,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,男人的死法有两种
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.86,0:10:49.58,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,一是位名誉而死 一是白白的牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.96,0:10:53.71,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,我想让有勇气真正的男儿光荣地死去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.97,0:10:55.24,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,光荣地死
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.65,0:10:59.10,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,他也是古拉多斯人 记住这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.68,0:11:01.51,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.05,0:11:07.48,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,大卫 罗安 听到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.48,0:11:08.59,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.59,0:11:12.57,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,敌人只想引我出来 所以我想请你们保护航天飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.57,0:11:15.13,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,英二 这时候不要再逞强了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.13,0:11:16.41,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,你一个人是办不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.41,0:11:20.40,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,听好了 我答应要保护大家的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.40,0:11:24.62,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,如果我被打倒的话 请你们跟地球的人们转达
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.62,0:11:28.58,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,为了让那个蔚蓝的星球一直闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.58,0:11:31.45,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,我想请你们帮帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.82,0:11:49.83,Default_Sub,Off,0,0,0,,卡露拉少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.53,0:11:53.95,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,行进中的轨道有地球的舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.04,0:12:15.46,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,什么 你说地球的舰队接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.72,0:12:17.93,Default_Sub,Off,0,0,0,,我传送影像给您看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.93,0:12:20.77,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,卡露拉 你先去跟地球的舰队作战
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.77,0:12:23.14,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,用你那边的主炮击沉大型母舰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.14,0:12:24.59,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.94,0:12:35.05,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,是地球军
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.14,0:12:38.20,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.20,0:12:40.37,Default_Sub,Elizavbeth,0,0,0,,地球舰队 请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.23,0:12:45.34,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,我是联合国的伊丽莎白·克蕾布里 请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.15,0:12:48.29,Default_Sub,Off,0,0,0,,伊丽莎白·克蕾布里 我们听得很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.54,0:12:50.72,Default_Sub,Off,0,0,0,,我是奥赛号的舰长撒扎兰多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.72,0:12:51.89,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.89,0:12:55.97,Default_Sub,Southerland,0,0,0,,刚才没回应你们 是为了防止敌人监听
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.60,0:13:01.25,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,我们坐的外星人航天飞机 正在被大型的追击队追击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.61,0:13:05.24,Default_Sub,Southerland,0,0,0,,我已知道你说的外星人 也就是敌人的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.24,0:13:06.66,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,我们马上就会展开攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.49,0:13:09.38,Default_Sub,Southerland,0,0,0,,我们也会保护你们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.84,0:13:13.25,Default_Sub,Southerland,0,0,0,,接下来你们就这样前往月球基地 祝你们好运
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.67,0:13:14.61,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,谢谢你 舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.92,0:13:17.86,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,没问题了 这下真的得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.57,0:13:24.68,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,盖尔前辈 这次对地球的军队
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.81,0:13:26.54,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,一定会毫不留情的攻过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.85,0:14:01.35,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,地球的人们 让你们看看我们古拉多斯真正的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.50,0:14:38.13,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,剩下的杂兵就交给你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.28,0:15:00.63,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,根本打不赢他们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.05,0:15:14.11,Default_Sub,Off,0,0,0,,地球军军舰进入射程范围
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.11,0:15:15.05,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,锁定他们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.05,0:15:17.05,Default_Sub,Com,0,0,0,,目标锁定完成
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.05,0:15:18.06,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,射击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.40,0:15:34.66,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,好鲜艳啊 做得好 卡露拉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.76,0:16:01.22,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,这才是 古拉多斯真正的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.93,0:16:11.67,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,不要 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.67,0:16:14.09,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,全灭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.09,0:16:15.65,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,真令人不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.10,0:16:46.01,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,给我出来 英二 碍事的家伙都没了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.53,0:16:57.92,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,伊丽莎白博士 你们尽可能躲开 大家就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.92,0:16:58.91,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,英二
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.06,0:17:03.85,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,看来你已有觉悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.85,0:17:04.79,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,盖尔前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.79,0:17:07.12,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,英二 没有人会来妨碍我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.01,0:17:14.24,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,永别了 英二
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.24,0:17:16.45,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,再见了 盖尔前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.46,0:17:29.22,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,他在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.22,0:17:33.32,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,太天真了 就连你背负着的地球一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.75,0:17:45.58,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,右边踝部中弹 损坏率0.02%
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.58,0:17:46.80,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,切换回路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.80,0:17:48.96,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,在31号处 有热源反应
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.38,0:17:58.53,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,你们不要出手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.69,0:18:09.44,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,左边上腕部中弹 损坏率0.25%
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.44,0:18:10.85,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,锁定目标
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.25,0:18:13.17,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,不能开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.15,0:18:19.33,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,腰部中弹 损坏率0.30%
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.33,0:18:21.55,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,英二 往右边闪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.55,0:18:23.28,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,大卫 罗安 走开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.45,0:18:30.37,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,英二 都要死了还逞强吗 命只有一条
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.37,0:18:34.59,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,对啊 虽然我也很害怕 但我们不能看同伴送死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.22,0:18:40.73,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,大卫 罗安
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.28,0:18:50.39,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,警告 马上撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.30,0:18:56.12,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,踝部中弹 损害严重
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.14,0:18:59.81,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,无法逃离敌人范围 快逃出本机
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.81,0:19:01.61,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,还没完
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.41,0:19:07.30,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,快逃出
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.30,0:19:09.95,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,怎么了 雷 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.75,0:19:14.63,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,你在干什么 雷 怎么了 雷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.32,0:19:18.59,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,中途逃脱一点都不像你 英二
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.32,0:19:21.53,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,原谅我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.01,0:20:34.39,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,盖尔中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.76,0:21:03.32,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,干得漂亮 英二
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.30,0:21:08.01,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,盖尔前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.74,0:21:12.36,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.36,0:21:15.60,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,SPT无法行动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.09,0:21:21.38,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,盖尔前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.38,0:21:32.52,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,这是多么美丽的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.31,0:21:38.68,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,那就是你拼死也要保护的 地球吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.86,0:21:42.37,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,那就是 你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.32,0:21:54.15,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,地球吗 玖丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.82,0:22:01.37,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,尽全力去救回中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.56,0:22:06.34,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,盖尔前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.59,0:22:13.30,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,不要管别的 派SPT去救中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.30,0:22:16.52,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,盖尔前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.40,0:22:25.53,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,在一闪一闪的星星之中 我们头一次听到那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.30,0:22:28.60,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,英二的哭声
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.23,0:22:35.60,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,好像野兽一般 好像小孩一样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.83,0:22:40.54,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,不 那是非常温柔的人 非常纯洁的灵魂发出的悲鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.54,0:22:44.38,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,也深深的震撼了我们的心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.01,0:23:58.15,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,住手 大卫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.15,0:24:00.50,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,那不是古拉多斯军 说不定是地球人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.08,0:24:01.91,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,地球人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.93,0:24:08.42,Layzner_Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs150\pos(720,790)}月球！ 请回答
